application_properties.label: DAPS JWKS URL
application_properties.tooltip: The URL to the DAPS JWKS endpoint.

application_properties.label: DAPS URL
application_properties.tooltip: The URL to the DAPS token endpoint.

application_properties.label: Enable DAPS Interaction
application_properties.tooltip: Enable interaction with DAPS for token validation.

application_properties.label: Extended Token Validation
application_properties.tooltip: Enable extended validation of tokens using DAPS. Performs additional checks on the token's validity like OCSP.

application_properties.label: Fetch Token on Startup
application_properties.tooltip: Fetch a DAPS token on application startup. This is useful if the application needs to interact with DAPS immediately after startup.

application_properties.label: Token Caching
application_properties.tooltip: Enable caching of DAPS tokens to avoid frequent requests to the DAPS server. This can improve performance but may lead to using stale tokens if not managed properly.

application_properties.label: Enable Authentication
application_properties.tooltip: Enable authentication for the application protocol. This setting controls whether the application requires authentication for accessing its resources.

application_properties.label: Dspace Version Auth profile
application_properties.tooltip: Dspace Version Authentication profile, comma separated list of strings
